Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼N大學社會學科第7屆親睦會現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「神臨」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.27,0:03:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨 請問一位嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是... 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想裡面應該...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 可以進去看下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.13,0:03:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.62,0:03:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我來遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是枸雅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.79,0:03:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢夥是誰來著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.21,0:03:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是今天的祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的...那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枸雅君?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去好認真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也是因為太沒用才被呼來喚去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枸雅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看史場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來我聽說史場她的老爸和你是同鄉?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個很小的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.21,0:04:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以彼此的感情都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛來東京的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他替我找了房子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.78,0:04:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各方面都很照顧我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你和史場念同一所大學只是巧合嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過史場日日乃她確實點數很高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告白的人全都被她甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學部裡的全員都粉身碎骨了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是今天輪到你出馬了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出馬?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯誼的時候某個人要去告白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是學部裡的規矩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這麼做過的只有你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她站起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個好機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快上快上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枸雅也要上洗手間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話對日日乃同學說...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我嗎 是什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實...那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.21,0:05:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 兩個人在這裡做些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說小詩 你醉得太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.49,0:05:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管醉成什麼樣都是我的自由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 小詩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在這裡吐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢夥是那種性格嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶 枸雅匡平
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小詩 你剛才吐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 那我就一口氣先乾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好勒 喝吧喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經怎樣都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.49,0:06:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去東京的大學?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡平...你...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許這樣也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你放棄了繼承{\c&H1414FF&}隻{\r}的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:30.49,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(768,655)}{\c&H1414FF&}せき
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也沒理由讓你繼續留在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看外面的世界也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你錯了 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就想離開這時間彷彿停滯不前一般的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:06:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.02,0:07:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為枸雅君你醉得不省人事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總不能放任著你不管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你醒了再一起匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是第二次對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年枸雅君來東京的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我家舉辦過歡迎會的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還被爸爸強行灌酒 結果醉得不省人事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說硬要勉強不勝酒力的人才是不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就在附近的居酒屋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說有具屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人事件?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說到處都是血
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼明天會再請二位到局裡說明情況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可以先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你去車站
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你特意送我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到發生這麼大的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到枸雅君居然這麼勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你遇到那樣的事情還能如此鎮定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.74,0:09:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這已經不是第一次了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耽誤你的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 那明天見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...日日乃同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...你多小心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 枸雅君也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到驚嚇 這也是理所當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她仍舊微笑著面對我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是她比我顯得可靠多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家紋...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是村子裡的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.82,0:10:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會在那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.89,0:10:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.63,0:10:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}玖吼理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:45.47,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}{\pos(640,655)}ククリ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.30,0:10:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你還是一樣做事很粗魯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.18,0:11:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你打扮得可真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有些過於花哨了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 反正比起神社的巫女服要好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去 熱可可
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.49,0:12:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才是準備接過杯子還是準備打碎它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪一個?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.39,0:12:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.66,0:12:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會和{\c&H1414FF&}案山子{\r}一起出現在這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.66,0:12:25.54,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,655)}{\c&H1414FF&}カカシ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經和村子裡的老規矩扯不上關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 這玩意兒可是村子裡的絕對秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可以被曝光的不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.33,0:12:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿幾他...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿幾?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那莫非在卡拉OK包廂裡的事...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是應該被關在牢裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一直被關在那裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但去年開始變得不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.37,0:13:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為牢房的人不小心說漏了嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他哥哥你已經離開了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.47,0:13:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那傢夥逃出去的理由是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「是因為我嗎」?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你在說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未免太瞧不起我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然派半吊子的小鬼來抓我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿幾..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 匡平 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然一個人擅自離開村子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:13:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開匡平
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在和匡平說話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃到一邊去 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手 詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就不可能被選中的古舊時代的{\c&H1414FF&}隻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:24.30,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1034,655)}{\c&H1414FF&}せき
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有這點程度罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你適可而止吧 阿幾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可和村子裡不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是可以隨意使用{\c&H1414FF&}案山子{\r}的地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:34.93,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(770,655)}{\c&H1414FF&}カカシ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼變得這麼畏畏縮縮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 枸雅先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的聲音是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.75,0:14:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為現在幾點了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 枸雅先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.15,0:14:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:14:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得你變得無趣了 匡平
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的話要更加...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許小看匡平
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼要說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手 你在做些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在這裡做些單調的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.51,0:15:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顧妹妹可真辛苦呢 匡平
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰奇怪的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 她還只是個孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是{\c&H1414FF&}隻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:40.56,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(688,655)}{\c&H1414FF&}せき
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是與{\c&H1414FF&}案山子{\r}心意相通的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:43.17,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(560,655)}{\c&H1414FF&}カカシ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太鈍了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再回去練練吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:15:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿幾...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都做了些什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用毫無力量的{\c&H1414FF&}隻{\r}對我動手動腳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:09.04,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,655)}{\c&H1414FF&}せき
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是她自找的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你生氣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.85,0:16:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就和我幹一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.61,0:16:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢夥已經瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘋狂的不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這村子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.66,0:16:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋 你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃開 匡平!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要炸飛你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.07,0:17:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?要住在日日乃...史場同學的家?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.39,0:17:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔...那樣太不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正有空閒的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有困難 總不能放著你不管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 我還是自己想辦法去找新的房子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是只有你一個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且神社那邊也聯繫我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託我照顧你們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神社那邊...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神社?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們把這個帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起乘車
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是擔心神社那邊的許可的話 已經允許了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時就留在你這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當是外出修行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們突然之間出現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也太自說自話了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神社的命令是絕對的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回現場去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸事件的當事人不在現場的話會被懷疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來即使來到大都市
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.22,0:18:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是得對他們言聽計從嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.74,0:18:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘋狂的不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這村子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿幾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.47,0:18:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我還是沒太搞清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神社之類的 村子之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前一次也沒有和我提起過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:19:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一時間理解不了那麼多的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枸雅君也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到神社的指示什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我一直希望能盡可能地避免你被牽扯進來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.83,0:19:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空守村啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自古以來就保護著十分重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 那東西現在是在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能為我叫出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.17,0:19:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放我下來...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃同學!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 你對日日乃同學做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神..明?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說我小時候的衣服也沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這就像連衣裙一樣 也很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是難以置信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然能憑自己的意識操縱這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 不准再做像剛才那樣的惡作劇了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.67,0:20:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐我真是嚇壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弄錯了讓它出來的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊 這東西果然很有壓迫感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是很佔空間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}玖吼理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:53.06,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}{\pos(640,655)}ククリ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的名字是{\c&H1414FF&}玖吼理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:56.33,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}{\pos(770,655)}ククリ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:20:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.06,0:21:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫{\c&H1414FF&}玖吼理{\r}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.06,0:21:01.43,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}{\pos(640,655)}ククリ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.72,0:21:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒睡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都要麻煩你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是獨生女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像是多了個妹妹一樣 很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽見你這麼說 真是幫了我大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...晚安了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.22,0:21:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枸雅君?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.49,0:21:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後就請你多多關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.31,0:21:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.64,0:21:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要受你照顧了

Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.30,0:23:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.96,0:23:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樣dolls終於開播了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.66,0:23:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這個單元
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖吼理也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.45,0:23:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個單元每週將由我和玖吼理
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.03,0:23:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為大家解說秘密的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.63,0:23:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖吼理也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.48,0:23:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 神明的特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.21,0:23:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,


Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:49.37,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}スイッチが入ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:56.47,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}世界の裏側を転がり落ちてくる　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:22:01.68,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あの橋の下の掃き溜めのように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.85,0:22:06.39,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}綺麗事で すまされない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:27.84,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}1から10まで　パーツ全部揃えても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:34.02,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今の私じゃ何も使えないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.99,0:22:38.19,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}手の腹を伝う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:43.01,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}てんとう虫の赤い点から
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.16,0:22:48.19,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}思わぬ火が付くこと恐れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.01,0:22:55.93,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}スイッチが入ったら　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.05,0:22:59.32,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}止まる思考回路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:03.00,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}手を引っ込めた途端　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.10,0:23:08.47,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}暗闇に逆に噛まれるような
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.73,0:23:13.10,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}遠すぎる景色がある
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:49.37,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}切入開關
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:56.47,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}翻轉起世界的背面　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:22:01.68,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仿若那座橋下的垃圾堆一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.85,0:22:06.39,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只憑借美麗的事物 亦無所終結
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:27.84,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即便從一至十 湊齊了全部部件
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:34.02,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如今的我亦無能為力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.99,0:22:38.19,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}以掌心傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:43.01,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在瓢蟲的紅點上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.16,0:22:48.19,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}附著著意想不到的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.01,0:22:55.93,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}切入開關
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.05,0:22:59.32,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}停止的思維
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:03.00,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}當我牽起你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.10,0:23:08.47,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}卻反被無盡黑暗所吞噬一般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.73,0:23:13.10,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那已太過遙遠的景色
